name: Threepio With His Parts Showing (AI)
Lore: 'Protocol droid designed by Anakin in order to help his mother. C-3P0 was not to be sold when Anakin left with Qui-Gon Jinn for Coruscant.',
Text: 'If in a battle with Shmi at a site, once per battle may place top card of your Used Pile on top of your Reserve Deck. Once per turn may place a card from hand on Used Pile to draw top card from Reserve Deck.',
